data.description: 5.7% interest rate FHA Assumable loan means you can take over the current loan at 5.7% interest!  Call your agent for details. Welcome home! This beautiful ranch style home sits on 1.45 acres located just minutes from I-35 in a gated community. You'll love the open concept kitchen equipped with modern appliances, granite countertops, walk-in pantry, and large island. The kitchen opens to your dining room and a large living area with a stunning stone fireplace and ample natural light. The master bedroom boasts an ensuite bathroom with a soaking tub, separate tiled shower, and walk in-closet. The closet features a pocket door directly to the laundry room which has tons of storage and a mud bench. There are 2 more spacious bedrooms and a 3rd flex room perfect for an office or gym. The 2nd bathroom has dual sinks and a tiled tub/shower combo. The garage has plenty of space for two vehicles and a workshop. The backyard oasis awaits you with a covered back porch, completely fenced yard and a dog run. This property offers a great opportunity to embrace the tranquility of rural living with an easy commute to the city.
